"title": "8486: spiritual warfare, armour",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8486: spiritual warfare, armour",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The armour of God refers to the resources that Christians possess for defending themselves against the attacks of the world, the flesh and the devil.</p>\n<h2>God is the believer's strength and shield</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps28:7-Ps28:8\">PSA 28:7–28:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:1\">GEN 15:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:29\">DEU 33:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps3:3\">PSA 3:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps7:10\">PSA 7:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:114\">PSA 119:114</a></p>\n<h2>Believers should be rightly clothed for battle</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:12-Rom13:14\">ROM 13:12–13:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:22-Eph4:24\">EPH 4:22–4:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:9\">COL 3:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:12-Col3:14\">COL 3:12–3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:1\">1PE 4:1</a></p>\n<h2>Believers should put on the full armour of God</h2>\n<h3>The belt of truth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:14\">EPH 6:14</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:95\">PSA 119:95</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:116\">PSA 119:116</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:14-Eph4:15\">EPH 4:14–4:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:8\">COL 2:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:13-2Tim1:14\">2TI 1:13–1:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:13\">1PE 1:13</a></p>\n<h3>The breastplate of righteousness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:14\">EPH 6:14</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:23\">PRO 4:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:6\">PRO 13:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:10\">ISA 61:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech3:1-Zech3:4\">ZEC 3:1–3:4</a></p>\n<h3>The gospel of peace</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:15\">EPH 6:15</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:27\">JHN 14:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:33\">JHN 16:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:6-Phil4:7\">PHP 4:6–4:7</a></p>\n<h3>The shield of faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:16\">EPH 6:16</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:17\">ROM 1:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:4\">HAB 2:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:9\">1PE 5:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:4\">1JN 5:4</a></p>\n<h3>The helmet of salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:17\">EPH 6:17</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:8-1Thess5:9\">1TH 5:8–5:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:11-Titus2:14\">TIT 2:11–2:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:3\">1JN 3:3</a></p>\n<h2>The Christian's spiritual weapons</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:4\">2CO 10:4</a></strong></p>\n<h3>The sword of the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:17\">EPH 6:17</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:11\">PSA 119:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:16-2Tim3:17\">2TI 3:16–3:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:12\">HEB 4:12</a></p>\n<h3>The armour of God is worn with prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:18\">EPH 6:18</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:16-Ps55:18\">PSA 55:16–55:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:16\">HEB 4:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:16\">JAS 5:16</a></p>",
